section.def:
licence
                (牌照) means a licence issued under section
                7(1);

ship
                (船舶) has the same meaning as in the Merchant
            Shipping (Registration) Ordinance (Cap. 415);

treating
                (加工處理) a whale includes storage for the purpose
            of treatment;

subsection.def:
fin whales (長鬚鯨)
                means whales known by any of the names set out in Part III of the
                    Schedule;
